    • compile

      public Map<String,Sequence> compile(Song song) throws InvalidMidiDataException, SymfonionException
      Compiles a Song object into a map from a port name to Sequence object.
      Parameters:
      song - An object that holds user-provided music data.
      Returns:
      A map from a port name to Sequence object.
      Throws:
      InvalidMidiDataException - Won't be thrown.
      SymfonionException - Undefined part name is referenced by a bar.
